[3] Report and Recommendation dated August 21, 1996 of Judge Abraham D. Caña; Id., pp. 32-41.

[4] Report and Recommendation dated December 13, 1996 of Judge Abraham D. Caña, Annex C.

[5] Id., Annex D.

[6] 249 SCRA 504 (1995).

[7] 220 SCRA 505 (1993).

